cdata.name: Credible
cdata.desc:
Based in Singapore, Credible is a business credit data platform. It enables users (businesses) with the tools to upload and store their credit-related data on a Blockchain-based environment. Credible stores and verifies the credit data from merchants and/or companies in order to assist them in achieving the pretended credit from lenders that can check the information on the platform with the users' authorization. The access to the businesses private credit data is paid by lenders with the PESA tokens.

The PESA token is an Ethereum-based (ERC-20) cryptocurrency. It is the token that fuels the platform as it is needed for the users to perform any transaction on Credible. In addition, the PESA tokens serve the lenders when paying for access to businesses credit data.
